onal"}, {"first_name": "Bryan", "last_name": "Masson", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "K\u00e9vin", "last_name": "Mauvieux", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Nicolas", "last_name": "Meizonnet", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Thibaut", "last_name": "Monnier", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Serge", "last_name": "Muller", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Jo\u00eblle", "last_name": "M\u00e9lin", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Ya\u00ebl", "last_name": "M\u00e9nach\u00e9", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Thomas", "last_name": "M\u00e9nag\u00e9", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Julien", "last_name": "Odoul", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Caroline", "last_name": "Parmentier", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Thierry", "last_name": "Perez", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "K\u00e9vin", "last_name": "Pfeffer", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Lisette", "last_name": "Pollet", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "St\u00e9phane", "last_name": "Rambaud", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Ang\u00e9lique", "last_name": "Ranc", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Julien", "last_name": "Rancoule", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Matthias", "last_name": "Renault", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Catherine", "last_name": "Rimbert", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Joseph", "last_name": "Rivi\u00e8re", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Laurence", "last_name": "Robert-Dehault", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "B\u00e9atrice", "last_name": "Roullaud", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Sophie-Laurence", "last_name": "Roy", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Ana\u00efs", "last_name": "Sabatini", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "\u00c9ric", "last_name": "Michoux", "party": "UDR"}, {"first_name": "Alexandre", "last_name": "Sabatou", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Emeric", "last_name": "Salmon", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Philippe", "last_name": "Schreck", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Anne", "last_name": "Sicard", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Emmanuel", "last_name": "Tach\u00e9 de la Pagerie", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Philippe", "last_name": "Tanguy", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Micha\u00ebl", "last_name": "Taverne", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Thierry", "last_name": "Tesson", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Lionel", "last_name": "Tivoli", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Romain", "last_name": "Tonussi", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Antoine", "last_name": "Villedieu", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric-Pierre", "last_name": "Vos", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric", "last_name": "Weber", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Charles", "last_name": "Alloncle", "party": "UDR"}], "summary": "Amendement de repli.\nCet amendement vise \u00e0 supprimer la CNDP.\nCr\u00e9\u00e9e en 1995, la commission nationale du d\u00e9bat public (CNDP) f\u00eatera bient\u00f4t ses trente ann\u00e9es d\u2019existence. Un tel recul permet au l\u00e9gislateur d\u2019interroger l\u2019utilit\u00e9 de cette autorit\u00e9 ind\u00e9pendante, particuli\u00e8rement \u00e0 l\u2019heure o\u00f9 la dette de la France a d\u00e9pass\u00e9 les 3 228 milliards d\u2019euros. En effet, si l\u2019heure est \u00e0 la r\u00e9duction des d\u00e9penses publiques, toute d\u00e9pense, et en particulier dans un comit\u00e9 que certains qualifient de \u00ab th\u00e9odule \u00bb, doit \u00eatre interrog\u00e9e. La suppression de la CNDP pourrait repr\u00e9senter en effet une \u00e9conomie de plus de 3,7 millions d\u2019euros annuels.\nMalgr\u00e9 ses trente ann\u00e9es d\u2019existence, la carence de notori\u00e9t\u00e9 de la CNDP doit interroger. Trop peu de Fran\u00e7ais connaissent cette autorit\u00e9 ind\u00e9pendante alors m\u00eame qu\u2019elle est cens\u00e9e \u00eatre l\u2019autorit\u00e9 pivot en charge de la participation du public dans le cadre de l\u2019\u00e9laboration de projets ou de politiques publiques qui ont des cons\u00e9quences sur l\u2019environnement.\nLa CNDP a \u00e9chou\u00e9 \u00e0 d\u00e9samorcer des situations conflictuelles li\u00e9es \u00e0 des projets ayant des cons\u00e9quences sur l\u2019environnement. Les exemples sont nombreux comme l\u2019\u2019a\u00e9roport du Grand Ouest \u00e0 Notre\u2011Dame des landes ou encore les mouvements d\u2019oppositions aux m\u00e9ga\u2011bassines comme \u00e0 Sainte\u2011Soline.\nPlus largement, la CNDP aurait pu assurer un r\u00f4le d\u2019instance d\u00e9mocratique plus large mais ne l\u2019a pas fait. En 2019, en pleine crise des gilets jaunes, il avait \u00e9t\u00e9 question de solliciter cette commission pour r\u00e9aliser un \u00ab grand d\u00e9bat national \u00bb. Madame Chantal Jouanno, alors pr\u00e9sidente de la CNDP, s\u2019\u00e9tait retir\u00e9e du pilotage de ce d\u00e9bat parce que les \u00ab conditions de s\u00e9r\u00e9nit\u00e9 n\u00e9cessaires pour ce d\u00e9bat [n\u2019\u00e9taient pas assur\u00e9es] \u00bb. C\u2019est donc un autre mod\u00e8le qu\u2019il faut trouver.\nPour toutes ces raisons, il convient \u00e0 l'alin\u00e9a premier de cet amendement de supprimer la Commission nationale du d\u00e9bat public. L\u2019alin\u00e9a\u00a0 2 ne rend pas la loi r\u00e9troactive et permet, quand la CNDP a d\u00e9j\u00e0 \u00e9t\u00e9 saisie, de maintenir le dispositif actuellement en place."}